title: Gold 5 - I'm Looking for a serious OCE Open Ladder team

body: I am a support main, but i can play top and mid almost as well, and can jungle and adc to quiet an extent, i'm looking for a team for the open ladder, i have a lot of experience with the game. Even if a gold is not what you need, just trial me and check me out, thanks.
